{"tid":635310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"星巴克全美分店下月停業半日進行反種族歧視培訓","createTime":"2018-04-20T04:31:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-20T05:16:07.000Z","uid":47352,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a19cb9e02fc8dd2c9a67457e79f856503e4d8c64","tid":635310,"uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:31:45.000Z","msg":"美國咖啡連鎖店星巴克宣布，全美國超過8千間分店下月29日下午停業半日，進行反種族歧視培訓，新入職員工亦會接受相關訓練，星克巴會將培訓經驗，與合作夥伴及其他公司分享。<br />\n<br />\n兩名黑人數日前在費城一間星巴克咖啡店等朋友，職員不讓他們使用洗手間，理由是他們沒有消費，分店經理其後報警，警方指兩名黑人非法入侵，拘捕他們，其後因證據不足將他們釋放。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n星巴克其後就事件道歉。"},{"pid":"4a3bef502169ee21e2316707e158afbd2b320754","tid":635310,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:33:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5361f3d1b56eaa9caf16cc9d222d39a9015cfa55","tid":635310,"uid":59192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:34:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17e8a8f29430e812abee89a7ab32cfd619a58cf8","tid":635310,"uid":52358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:34:53.000Z","msg":"力架成日逆向歧視白鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3614a811bb1286cfef457e62bf85be60498cac29","tid":635310,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:37:24.000Z","msg":"件事係咪個黑人冇買野用廁所，叫佢走又唔肯走先報警"},{"pid":"d730a22f77009b35cd0cecd1cd6589dc04602414","tid":635310,"uid":123711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:39:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9416f9043718a6607389b88fdc9cda3c20f9f21e","tid":635310,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T05:16:07.000Z","msg":"星巴克都唔識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n趁呢件事抽水話 我地趕啲無消費既人走係為左提供更好既俾消費者<br />\n啲人見無黑鬼支那人去座 生意一定仲好"}]}